sequenceDiagram
    actor Diner
    participant App
    participant API
    participant Session
    participant POS
    participant Room
    participant Tab
    participant Checkout
    participant History

    Diner->>App: Sign in
    App->>API: Login request
    API-->>App: Demo user and token
    Diner->>App: Open Live Tab
    App->>Session: Start session
    Session->>Tab: Create empty tab
    Session-->>App: Return session id
    App->>Room: Subscribe to session room
    POS->>API: Send staged order update
    API->>Tab: Replace tab items and recalculate totals
    API->>Room: Emit tab update
    Room-->>App: Tab updated event
    App->>API: Fetch latest tab
    API-->>App: Current tab data
    Checkout->>Tab: Mark tab paid
    Checkout->>History: Write receipt and loyalty points
